IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. CONTRACTED TEST.

DATA DIVISION.
01 X PICTURE IS 999.
01 Y PICTURE IS 999.
01 Z PICTURE IS 999.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.

MOVE 10 TO X
MOVE 20 TO Y
MOVE 80 TO Z

IF X = 10 OR X = 20 THEN
    DISPLAY "NORMAL OR"
END

IF X = 10 OR 20 THEN
    DISPLAY "CONTRACTED OR VALUE"
END

IF X > 10 AND X < 20 THEN
    DISPLAY "NORMAL RANGE"
END

IF X > 10 AND < 20 THEN
    DISPLAY "CONTRACTED RANGE"
END

IF X > 10 AND X < 20 OR X < 100 AND X > 80 THEN
    DISPLAY "NORMAL COMPLEX"
END

IF X > 10 AND < 20 OR 100 AND > 80 THEN
    DISPLAY "CONTRACTED COMPLEX"
END

EVALUATE X
    WHEN 10 OR 20
        DISPLAY "EVALUATE CONTRACTED VALUES"
    WHEN OTHER
        DISPLAY "OTHER"
END

EVALUATE X ALSO Y
    WHEN 10 ALSO 20
        DISPLAY "EVALUATE ALSO"
END

LOOP
    VARYING X FROM 1 TO 5 BY 1
    DISPLAY X
END

LOOP
    DISPLAY X
    WHILE X < 10
    ADD 1 TO X
END

LOOP
    DISPLAY X
    ADD 1 TO X
    UNTIL X = 20
END

LOOP
    VARYING X
    DISPLAY X
END

STOP.